OL,3,CChris Thomas sacked from Manx health
OL,4,Cdepartment after two and a half weeks
OL,6,FTalking of his dismissal, Mr Cannan
OL,7,Fsaid: "It is regrettable that Mr
OL,8,FThomas's recent actions have required
OL,9,Fthe Council of Ministers to take this
OL,10,Fstep.
OL,12,F"The Government Code clearly sets out
OL,13,Fthe importance of a positive and
OL,14,Fproductive relationship between a
OL,15,FMinister and Members of a Government
OL,16,FDepartment.
